<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type"/>
        <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting"/>
    </head>
    <body class="bg-white font-sans">
        <div class="max-w-xl pt-5 pb-12 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-2xl pt-4">
                Hi {{ email.toName }},
            </h1>

            <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
                Someone recently requested a password change for your Dropbox account. If this was you, you can set a
                new password here:
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
                Remember to use a password that is both strong and unique to your Twitch account.
            </p>

            <section class="py-7">
                <a href="{{ url('app_reset_password') }}"
                   class="bg-black rounded-sm font-semibold text-white text-sm no-underline text-center block px-6 py-3">
                    Reset password
                </a>
            </section>

            <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
                However if you did NOT perform this password change, just ignore and delete this message.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
                Best,
                <br/>â€” The Shape of You team
            </p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
